   ACCESSIBILITY

      The Interagency Coordinating Committee on the Validation of Alternative
      Methods (ICCVAM) is making every effort to ensure that the information
      on our website is accessible to all. If you use special adaptive
      equipment to access the Web and encounter problems with our site,
      please let us know by writing to NICEATM or submitting your suggestions
      or recommendations using the comments page. Please be as detailed as
      possible when describing the information you need.

      To learn more about the regulations governing the accessibility of
      Federal electronic information products, visit the Section 508 page.

      The following on-line conversion tools are linked here for your
      convenience:
        * Adobe PDF translators to convert PDF files to HTML or ASCII text:
             + Adobe On-line URL Submission Form [PDF to HTML]
             + Adobe PDF conversion by email [PDF to HTML or text]
        * HTML Stripper [removes HTML coding from text]

   Thank you for visiting the ICCVAM website.
